(* --- PASS: reminder_plan --- *)
<dose> is a unit:
    plural is <doses>.

<taken> is a number:
    valid values:
        0 <doses> ... 1 <dose>.

<Daily reminder> is a plan:
    before plan:
        <taken> = 1 <dose>.
        assess <taken>:
            0 <doses>:
                information "Missed".
            1 <dose>:
                information "On track".

(* --- PASS: morning_checkin --- *)
<morning> is a period:
    timeframe:
        between Monday ... Friday; 08:00 ... 09:00.

<Morning check-in> is a plan:
    before plan:
        information "Plan started".

    <check in> with begin of <morning>:
        information "Good morning".

(* --- FAIL: missing_question_property --- *)
<age> is a number:
    valid values:
        1 year ... 10 years.

<Missing question> is a plan:
    before plan:
        ask for <age>.
